libtctl: libtctl (Gobject Bluetooth Controller)
libtctl:
libtctl: This library is intended to provide a GLib style library of 
libtctl: application support for accessing common platform Bluetooth functions 
libtctl: under Linux, and is used by GNOME Bluetooth applications and GNOME Phone 
libtctl: Manager require. It can also be used as a stand alone library as it does 
libtctl: not require GNOME libraries.
libtctl: 
libtctl: For more information, please see http://live.gnome.org/GnomeBluetooth
